metadata.description: Tedy is a clueless guy and likes to live life as she wants, you know that person with a crazy face but who is everywhere, well this crazy person in the neighborhood can be boring but he knows how to get everywhere with the his crazy way of being, he knows how to be cool and no matter what occasion he's in, this collection will be crazy and fun at the same time.
